{
  "texts": [
    "A similar approach is considered in ref.",
    "85 where a 640×480 pixels image is captured by an image sensor and then resized to a 16×16 image.",
    "The resizing procedure and the need of such a procedure will be covered later in this Sub- section.",
    "Both cases consider an FPGA in order interface the image acquisition system (i.e.",
    "CMOS image sensor and the resizing algorithm) with the memristor crossbar and its peripheral circuitry."
  ]
}